  m_Name: BigEye_1_Offer
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogData
  Lines:
  - I used to be a beginner like you, then I learned the secret of this world.
  - I unlocked my third eye and now I can use powerful magic.
  - As a fellow adventurer, I'm willing to teach you, for a price of course.
  - Go get some furs from the bunnies around here. I need 10 of them for the ritual.
